headline: Is McDonald's (MCD) Price Justified After Strong Multi Year Share Gains?
summary: If you are wondering whether McDonald's stock still offers value at current levels, this article will walk through what the numbers actually say about its price. The share price most recently closed at US$327.16, with returns of 3.9% over 7 days, 6.5% over 30 days, 7.9% year to date, 13.8% over 1 year, 33.6% over 3 years and 71.4% over 5 years. Recent attention on McDonald's has focused on how the brand is positioning itself within global quick service dining and on ongoing discussions...
